WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:04.960
The Barclays app

2
00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:07.440
How to redeem Apple TV+

3
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:12.600
To redeem Apple TV+ on the
Barclays app, start by logging in

4
00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:15.520
and from the home screen, tap ‘Products’.

5
00:00:15.840 --> 00:00:18.280
Next, tap ‘Blue Rewards’

6
00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:21.680
then tap ‘Apple TV+’ from the list.

7
00:00:21.680 --> 00:00:26.720
Here, you’ll see a summary of what you can
get with an Apple TV+ subscription.

8
00:00:26.720 --> 00:00:29.600
You can see the most
frequently asked questions here

9
00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:31.760
and all FAQs here.

10
00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:35.680
If you’re happy, select the
subscription you’d like to redeem.

11
00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:38.680
The app will now set up your subscription.

12
00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:42.080
Tap on ‘Complete setup’ to confirm.

13
00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:46.520
We’ll now show you how to set up
your subscription on an iOS device.

14
00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:49.680
Tap ‘OK’ if you’re happy to leave the Barclays app.

15
00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:52.760
You’ll be taken to the Apple TV+ homepage

16
00:00:52.760 --> 00:00:56.120
where you can watch award-winning
Apple Original series and films.

17
00:00:56.440 --> 00:01:00.880
If you’re on an Android device, this part
of the journey is slightly different.

18
00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:03.320
When you tap ‘Get Apple TV+’

19
00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:06.680
you’ll be sent to the Apple
TV mobile webpage.

20
00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:10.120
If you don’t have an account, tap ‘Sign up’.

21
00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:11.960
Add your details

22
00:01:21.240 --> 00:01:23.680
and agree to the Terms and Conditions.

23
00:01:24.120 --> 00:01:26.200
Then enter your Apple ID.

24
00:01:31.120 --> 00:01:32.720
The first time you log in

25
00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:36.440
you’ll be sent a six-digit verification
code to your mobile.

26
00:01:36.440 --> 00:01:39.240
Enter it here and tap ‘Continue’.

27
00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:44.080
You’ll now be taken to the Apple TV+ homepage

28
00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:48.800
where you can watch award-winning
Apple Original series and films.

